319
00:21:01,759 --> 00:21:08,019
[SPEAKER_00] ako gospodin htjedne živećemo i činiti ovo ili ono.

320
00:21:08,019 --> 00:21:11,779
[SPEAKER_00] Jakov nije rekao da ne smijemo planirati,

321
00:21:11,779 --> 00:21:15,220
[SPEAKER_00] ali ono što kaže da ne možemo biti sigurni u te planove,

322
00:21:15,220 --> 00:21:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] kaže činite dobro dok traje ono danas.

323
00:21:17,539 --> 00:21:19,940
[SPEAKER_00] Činite dobro dok možeš.

324
00:21:20,839 --> 00:21:26,039
[SPEAKER_00] za koje jedino vrijeme u koje možeš biti siguran

325
00:21:26,039 --> 00:21:27,940
[SPEAKER_00] je ovo sad koje imaš.

326
00:21:27,940 --> 00:21:31,019
[SPEAKER_00] Čini ono sad što možeš.

327
00:21:31,019 --> 00:21:32,240
[SPEAKER_00] Sad u ovom trenutku.

328
00:21:32,240 --> 00:21:33,059
[SPEAKER_00] Koje jedino sigurno?

329
00:21:33,059 --> 00:21:35,180
[SPEAKER_00] Sutra? Ja želim se sutra probuditi.

330
00:21:35,180 --> 00:21:36,339
[SPEAKER_00] Ja imam planove za sutra.

331
00:21:36,339 --> 00:21:39,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi, kasnim zbog glasa, kasnim se snimanjima,

332
00:21:39,019 --> 00:21:40,720
[SPEAKER_00] trebam mi sporučiti lekcije.

333
00:21:40,720 --> 00:21:41,420
[SPEAKER_00] Imam stvari.

334
00:21:41,420 --> 00:21:43,640
[SPEAKER_00] Imam planove koje trebam odraditi.

335
00:21:43,640 --> 00:21:45,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ali znate što sam jedino siguran?

336
00:21:45,440 --> 00:21:47,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam siguran jedino u ovoj trenutak

337
00:21:47,119 --> 00:21:48,079
[SPEAKER_00] gdje sad stojem pred vama

338
00:21:48,079 --> 00:21:49,400
[SPEAKER_00] i trebam vam prenijeti Božu riječ.

339
00:21:50,839 --> 00:21:52,599
[SPEAKER_00] Šta ako je to zadnje što ću napraviti?

340
00:21:52,599 --> 00:21:55,140
[SPEAKER_00] Bolje da bi bolje dobro prenesem.

341
00:21:55,140 --> 00:21:57,819
[SPEAKER_00] Druga stvar.

342
00:21:57,819 --> 00:22:01,759
[SPEAKER_00] Isus kaže, ne budite dakle zabranuti za sutra.

343
00:22:01,759 --> 00:22:04,200
[SPEAKER_00] Jer će se sutra brinuti samo za sebe.

344
00:22:04,200 --> 00:22:06,519
[SPEAKER_00] Dosta je danu zla njegova.

345
00:22:06,519 --> 00:22:09,200
[SPEAKER_00] Tražite najprije kraljastvo Božje

346
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:10,559
[SPEAKER_00] i njegovu pravednost,

347
00:22:10,559 --> 00:22:12,220
[SPEAKER_00] a sve će vam se ostalo nadodati.

348
00:22:18,339 --> 00:22:20,160
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ne možeš riješiti

349
00:22:20,160 --> 00:22:21,980
[SPEAKER_00] mjesec dana u naprijed

350
00:22:21,980 --> 00:22:23,299
[SPEAKER_00] sa svojom brigom,

351
00:22:23,299 --> 00:22:25,400
[SPEAKER_00] jer imaš dovoljno Božje milosti

352
00:22:25,400 --> 00:22:26,279
[SPEAKER_00] za ono danas.

353
00:22:26,279 --> 00:22:27,740
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što ti je,

354
00:22:27,740 --> 00:22:29,299
[SPEAKER_00] kad mi je jako teško,

355
00:22:29,299 --> 00:22:31,420
[SPEAKER_00] onda si počinjem posvješćivati kao

356
00:22:31,420 --> 00:22:33,759
[SPEAKER_00] imam dovoljno snage

357
00:22:33,759 --> 00:22:35,180
[SPEAKER_00] za ovo što je sad ispred mene.

358
00:22:35,180 --> 00:22:36,880
[SPEAKER_00] Imam dovoljno snage

359
00:22:36,880 --> 00:22:38,660
[SPEAKER_00] izdržati ovo sad.

360
00:22:38,660 --> 00:22:40,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo u ovom trenutku,

361
00:22:40,460 --> 00:22:41,380
[SPEAKER_00] koliko god mi je teško,

362
00:22:41,380 --> 00:22:42,400
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam siguran,

363
00:22:42,400 --> 00:22:43,559
[SPEAKER_00] kaže Bože reći,

364
00:22:43,559 --> 00:22:45,740
[SPEAKER_00] Bože milost je nova svakoga jutra,

365
00:22:46,059 --> 00:22:47,200
[SPEAKER_00] imam dovoljno snage

366
00:22:47,200 --> 00:22:48,720
[SPEAKER_00] za ovo sad što prolazim.

367
00:22:48,720 --> 00:22:50,640
[SPEAKER_00] Dovoljno snage.

368
00:22:50,640 --> 00:22:51,960
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje god da se nalaziš,

369
00:22:51,960 --> 00:22:53,140
[SPEAKER_00] imaš dovoljno snage

370
00:22:53,140 --> 00:22:54,559
[SPEAKER_00] za ovo gdje se sad nalaziš.

371
00:22:54,559 --> 00:22:55,480
[SPEAKER_00] Za danas.

372
00:22:55,480 --> 00:22:57,180
[SPEAKER_00] Za sutra ćeš dobiti novu snagu.

373
00:22:57,180 --> 00:22:58,839
[SPEAKER_00] Ali imaš dovoljno za danas.

374
00:22:58,839 --> 00:23:00,119
[SPEAKER_00] 100%.

375
00:23:00,119 --> 00:23:03,339
[SPEAKER_00] I ono što Isus govori ovdje,

376
00:23:03,339 --> 00:23:04,880
[SPEAKER_00] ne razmišljaj,

377
00:23:04,880 --> 00:23:07,180
[SPEAKER_00] je li posao A ili B za mene,

378
00:23:07,180 --> 00:23:08,880
[SPEAKER_00] nego je li tvoje srce ispravno.

379
00:23:08,880 --> 00:23:11,119
[SPEAKER_00] Tražite najprije Bože kraljestvo,

380
00:23:11,119 --> 00:23:13,079
[SPEAKER_00] sve ostalo će se nadodati.

381
00:23:13,079 --> 00:23:15,859
[SPEAKER_00] Je li tvoje srce ispravno?

382
00:23:17,000 --> 00:23:19,259
[SPEAKER_00] Je li tvoje srce usmjereno na Bože kraljestvo?

383
00:23:19,259 --> 00:23:21,740
[SPEAKER_00] Pa je li onda A ili B?

384
00:23:21,740 --> 00:23:22,680
[SPEAKER_00] Pa tak sve jedno.

385
00:23:22,680 --> 00:23:25,200
[SPEAKER_00] Ali je li tvoje srce usmjereno na Bože kraljestvo?

386
00:23:25,200 --> 00:23:25,740
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

387
00:23:25,740 --> 00:23:29,319
[SPEAKER_00] Pa onda Božja volja za tvoj život je i ja i B.

388
00:23:29,319 --> 00:23:31,519
[SPEAKER_00] Pričao sam bit će na konferenciji.

389
00:23:31,519 --> 00:23:33,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam sanjao o korporaciji, bankama,

390
00:23:33,900 --> 00:23:34,619
[SPEAKER_00] o dijelima,

391
00:23:34,619 --> 00:23:37,660
[SPEAKER_00] o tim nekim menadžerskim firmama

392
00:23:37,660 --> 00:23:38,839
[SPEAKER_00] i ulogama i tako dalje.

393
00:23:38,839 --> 00:23:40,599
[SPEAKER_00] Je li bi se ja ostvario u tom poslu?

394
00:23:40,599 --> 00:23:42,180
[SPEAKER_00] Sigurno.

395
00:23:42,180 --> 00:23:43,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ja bi uživao u tome.

396
00:23:43,940 --> 00:23:45,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ja volim te stvari.

397
00:23:45,200 --> 00:23:49,299
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam se ja ostvario u ovom poslanju.

398
00:23:49,299 --> 00:23:50,059
[SPEAKER_00] I ja sam.

399
00:23:50,059 --> 00:23:53,819
[SPEAKER_00] Mogu sam izabrati šta god sam htio.

400
00:23:53,819 --> 00:23:56,759
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne vjerujem, danas ne vjerujem,

401
00:23:56,759 --> 00:23:58,240
[SPEAKER_00] da bi mi Bog rekao, znaš šta,

402
00:23:58,240 --> 00:23:59,660
[SPEAKER_00] imao sam nešto bolje za tebe.

403
00:24:02,140 --> 00:24:04,859
[SPEAKER_00] Kao ono, pokvario mi je svu sreću gdje sam trenutno.

404
00:24:04,859 --> 00:24:07,180
[SPEAKER_00] Zavisite da mi sad kaže,

405
00:24:07,180 --> 00:24:07,619
[SPEAKER_00] Marko,

406
00:24:07,619 --> 00:24:10,519
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu si puno više.

407
00:24:10,519 --> 00:24:12,960
[SPEAKER_00] Pa koliko je tu depresivno

408
00:24:12,960 --> 00:24:15,720
[SPEAKER_00] razmišljati cijelo vrijeme,

409
00:24:15,720 --> 00:24:17,579
[SPEAKER_00] da bi mi Bog mogu u bilo kojem trenutku reći,

410
00:24:17,579 --> 00:24:18,279
[SPEAKER_00] Marko, znaš šta,

411
00:24:18,279 --> 00:24:19,259
[SPEAKER_00] mogao si bolje.

412
00:24:19,259 --> 00:24:21,059
[SPEAKER_00] Kao, imao si srce,

413
00:24:21,059 --> 00:24:22,059
[SPEAKER_00] da si me htio slijede,

414
00:24:22,059 --> 00:24:23,140
[SPEAKER_00] da si htio Božu volju,

415
00:24:23,140 --> 00:24:25,819
[SPEAKER_00] da si htio mene na prvom mjestu,

416
00:24:26,160 --> 00:24:26,640
[SPEAKER_00] ali znaš šta,

417
00:24:26,640 --> 00:24:30,420
[SPEAKER_00] je, pa sam ti rekao da ideš na drugi natječaj.

418
00:24:30,420 --> 00:24:34,339
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nije Bog takav.

419
00:24:34,339 --> 00:24:37,059
[SPEAKER_00] Nije Bog takav.

420
00:24:37,059 --> 00:24:39,839
[SPEAKER_00] Pavao kada govori

421
00:24:39,839 --> 00:24:41,519
[SPEAKER_00] o Božoj volji,

422
00:24:41,519 --> 00:24:43,839
[SPEAKER_00] znači on ne govori o karijeri,

423
00:24:43,839 --> 00:24:45,900
[SPEAKER_00] nego o posvećenju.

424
00:24:45,900 --> 00:24:47,839
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, ne suobličujte se ovom svijetu,

425
00:24:47,839 --> 00:24:49,140
[SPEAKER_00] nego se preobražavajte

426
00:24:49,140 --> 00:24:51,539
[SPEAKER_00] obnavljanjem svoga uma,

427
00:24:51,539 --> 00:24:53,579
[SPEAKER_00] da mognete razabrati što je volja Bože,

428
00:24:53,579 --> 00:24:55,559
[SPEAKER_00] što je dobro, Bogu milo i savršeno.

429
00:24:56,160 --> 00:24:57,859
[SPEAKER_00] Pazite dakle, kako živite,

430
00:24:57,859 --> 00:24:58,960
[SPEAKER_00] iskupljujte vrijeme,

431
00:24:58,960 --> 00:25:00,819
[SPEAKER_00] shvatite što je volja Gospodnja.

432
00:25:00,819 --> 00:25:05,119
[SPEAKER_00] Sad u ovom trenutku,

433
00:25:05,119 --> 00:25:06,480
[SPEAKER_00] oprostit nekome,

434
00:25:06,480 --> 00:25:08,480
[SPEAKER_00] to je Božja volja za tvoj život,

435
00:25:08,480 --> 00:25:09,660
[SPEAKER_00] sad u ovom trenutku.

436
00:25:09,660 --> 00:25:11,440
[SPEAKER_00] Pomoć nekome,

437
00:25:11,440 --> 00:25:13,220
[SPEAKER_00] to je Božja volja za tvoj život,

438
00:25:13,220 --> 00:25:14,160
[SPEAKER_00] sada u ovom trenutku.

439
00:25:14,160 --> 00:25:16,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što je sad ispred tebe,

440
00:25:16,039 --> 00:25:19,059
[SPEAKER_00] zahvaljivati u svim okolnostima,

441
00:25:19,059 --> 00:25:20,579
[SPEAKER_00] biti ljubazan prema drugima,

442
00:25:20,579 --> 00:25:22,480
[SPEAKER_00] služiti danas.

443
00:25:22,480 --> 00:25:25,920
[SPEAKER_00] Služiti danas.

444
00:25:26,160 --> 00:25:29,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ono u čemu si siguran da imaš.

445
00:25:29,079 --> 00:25:33,400
[SPEAKER_00] Božja volja se više tiče toga

446
00:25:33,400 --> 00:25:34,880
[SPEAKER_00] tko postajemo,

447
00:25:34,880 --> 00:25:37,619
[SPEAKER_00] nego što radimo ili gdje živimo.

448
00:25:42,619 --> 00:25:47,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ne postoji samo jedna savršena osoba za tebe.

449
00:25:47,460 --> 00:25:53,259
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerojatno možeš u životu funkcionirati

450
00:25:53,259 --> 00:25:55,240
[SPEAKER_00] puno više ljudi nek što misliš da bi mogao

451
00:25:55,240 --> 00:25:56,619
[SPEAKER_00] do kraja života funkcionirati.

452
00:25:56,619 --> 00:25:59,140
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ako razmišljaš da samo ta jedna osoba

453
00:25:59,140 --> 00:26:00,079
[SPEAKER_00] je samo za tebe,

454
00:26:00,079 --> 00:26:03,740
[SPEAKER_00] onda ćeš provesti život tražiči samo tu jednu osobu,

455
00:26:03,859 --> 00:26:05,759
[SPEAKER_00] misliš da onda će sve biti super.

456
00:26:05,759 --> 00:26:14,759
[SPEAKER_00] Partnerski odnos je nešto na čemu trebamo raditi.

457
00:26:14,759 --> 00:26:19,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ne postoji samo jedan posao koji moramo raditi,

458
00:26:19,259 --> 00:26:20,319
[SPEAKER_00] koji ćemo raditi.

459
00:26:21,099 --> 00:26:31,240
[SPEAKER_00] Da mi je tad neko rekao da će za par godina

460
00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:32,539
[SPEAKER_00] sve ovo ovako izgledat,

461
00:26:32,539 --> 00:26:33,640
[SPEAKER_00] ja ne bih vjerovao.

462
00:26:33,640 --> 00:26:37,339
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi moji, da je meni neko prije šest mjeseci

463
00:26:37,339 --> 00:26:39,720
[SPEAKER_00] rekao da ću ja raditi stvari koje sad radim,

464
00:26:39,720 --> 00:26:43,140
[SPEAKER_00] ja bih rekao, ma ne.

465
00:26:43,140 --> 00:26:45,019
[SPEAKER_00] Nema šanse.

466
00:26:45,019 --> 00:26:46,660
[SPEAKER_00] Ma nisam to ja.

467
00:26:46,660 --> 00:26:49,299
[SPEAKER_00] Nema šanse da se to dogodi.

468
00:26:49,299 --> 00:26:51,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ne može to biti.

469
00:26:51,099 --> 00:26:54,400
[SPEAKER_00] Samo unazad šest mjeseci.

470
00:26:54,400 --> 00:26:56,279
[SPEAKER_00] Samo unazad četiri mjeseca daje daje.

471
00:26:56,279 --> 00:26:58,660
[SPEAKER_00] Samo unazad četiri mjeseca daje neko,

472
00:26:58,660 --> 00:27:00,920
[SPEAKER_00] e Marko, za četiri mjeseca će ti život izgledati

473
00:27:00,920 --> 00:27:02,200
[SPEAKER_00] ovako, ovako, ovako, ovako.

474
00:27:02,200 --> 00:27:04,119
[SPEAKER_00] Sve ono što mi se sad trenutno događa.

475
00:27:04,119 --> 00:27:04,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ja rekao, ma ne.

476
00:27:04,920 --> 00:27:08,519
[SPEAKER_00] Kao možda, pa nadam se,

477
00:27:08,519 --> 00:27:09,960
[SPEAKER_00] pa bilo bi super, ali ne.

478
00:27:09,960 --> 00:27:12,680
[SPEAKER_00] E sad šta se dogodilo?

479
00:27:12,680 --> 00:27:15,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ja gledam šta trebam napraviti

480
00:27:15,119 --> 00:27:16,519
[SPEAKER_00] i šta ja znam.

481
00:27:16,519 --> 00:27:18,640
[SPEAKER_00] Nedavno sam razgovarao s jednom osobom

482
00:27:18,640 --> 00:27:19,279
[SPEAKER_00] i rekao sam joj,

483
00:27:19,640 --> 00:27:22,680
[SPEAKER_00] ako ti znaš, trenutno imaš spozna i o tome,

484
00:27:22,680 --> 00:27:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] da vidiš samo do oneh tamo orkulja,

485
00:27:26,000 --> 00:27:26,799
[SPEAKER_00] šta god da je ono.

486
00:27:26,799 --> 00:27:28,460
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, Darija vidim kroz ovo stan.

487
00:27:28,460 --> 00:27:30,299
[SPEAKER_00] Da vidim samo do tamo.

488
00:27:30,299 --> 00:27:33,160
[SPEAKER_00] I to je sve što ja znam da trebam napraviti.

489
00:27:33,160 --> 00:27:35,099
[SPEAKER_00] Pa šta ću napraviti?

490
00:27:36,039 --> 00:27:37,039
[SPEAKER_00] Oteći ću do tamo.

491
00:27:37,039 --> 00:27:44,299
[SPEAKER_00] I onda kad dođem do ovdje,

492
00:27:44,299 --> 00:27:45,980
[SPEAKER_00] šta se dogodilo?

493
00:27:45,980 --> 00:27:48,259
[SPEAKER_00] Sad vidim i ona vrata.

494
00:27:48,259 --> 00:27:51,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ne vidim tamo, ne vidim tamo,

495
00:27:51,599 --> 00:27:52,579
[SPEAKER_00] vidim do onih vrata.

496
00:27:52,579 --> 00:27:54,480
[SPEAKER_00] Šta ću napraviti sada?

497
00:27:54,480 --> 00:27:56,680
[SPEAKER_00] Pa otići ću do tih vrata.

498
00:27:56,680 --> 00:27:59,319
[SPEAKER_00] I onda ću vidjeti ta vrata

499
00:27:59,319 --> 00:28:01,759
[SPEAKER_00] i otvorit ću ta vrata.

500
00:28:01,759 --> 00:28:03,599
[SPEAKER_00] I šta će se onda dogoditi?

501
00:28:03,599 --> 00:28:05,900
[SPEAKER_00] Onda ću vidjeti cijelo dvorište.

502
00:28:05,900 --> 00:28:08,059
[SPEAKER_00] I šta onda?

503
00:28:08,059 --> 00:28:10,079
[SPEAKER_00] Onda ću vidjeti do drugih vrata.

504
00:28:10,079 --> 00:28:11,640
[SPEAKER_00] Onda ću vidjeti do drugog zavoja.

505
00:28:11,640 --> 00:28:12,880
[SPEAKER_00] Onda ću, šta ću onda napraviti?

506
00:28:12,880 --> 00:28:14,779
[SPEAKER_00] Bože, di sada idem?

507
00:28:14,779 --> 00:28:15,980
[SPEAKER_00] Di ću sad završiti?

508
00:28:16,819 --> 00:28:17,440
[SPEAKER_00] Uvijek desno.

509
00:28:17,440 --> 00:28:23,359
[SPEAKER_00] Vidim, odem dokud vidim.

510
00:28:23,359 --> 00:28:25,740
[SPEAKER_00] I dođem tamo i šta će se onda dogoditi?

511
00:28:25,740 --> 00:28:26,859
[SPEAKER_00] I onda vidim dalje.

512
00:28:26,859 --> 00:28:29,359
[SPEAKER_00] I onda šta ću onda napraviti?

513
00:28:29,359 --> 00:28:31,680
[SPEAKER_00] Pa otići ću dokud vidim.

514
00:28:31,680 --> 00:28:34,720
[SPEAKER_00] I onda kad dođem tamo, šta ću onda vidjeti?

515
00:28:34,720 --> 00:28:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] Onda ću vidjeti još dalje.

516
00:28:35,960 --> 00:28:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta sam napravio u svome životu

517
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:42,440
[SPEAKER_00] nakon tog njegovog razgovora do ovog danas?

518
00:28:42,440 --> 00:28:45,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što sam znao da trebam u tom trenutku raditi.

519
00:28:46,819 --> 00:28:52,140
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što znam da je sad Bože volja za moj život.

520
00:28:52,140 --> 00:28:54,559
[SPEAKER_00] Sad snimi program.

521
00:28:54,559 --> 00:28:55,900
[SPEAKER_00] Napiši ovo.

522
00:28:55,900 --> 00:28:57,140
[SPEAKER_00] Pravi objev.

523
00:28:57,140 --> 00:28:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Stavi ovo.

524
00:28:58,000 --> 00:28:59,059
[SPEAKER_00] Napravi ovo.

525
00:28:59,059 --> 00:29:00,119
[SPEAKER_00] Zapiši ovo.

526
00:29:00,119 --> 00:29:01,319
[SPEAKER_00] Odradi susret.

527
00:29:01,319 --> 00:29:03,359
[SPEAKER_00] Šta god trenutno daje u mom životu.

528
00:29:03,359 --> 00:29:06,180
[SPEAKER_00] Šta ću napraviti svaki dan?

529
00:29:06,180 --> 00:29:07,480
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki dan ću to napraviti.

530
00:29:07,480 --> 00:29:09,619
[SPEAKER_00] Sve šta vidim da...

531
00:29:09,619 --> 00:29:11,140
[SPEAKER_00] Šta će se onda dogoditi?

532
00:29:11,140 --> 00:29:12,980
[SPEAKER_00] Onda će se otvoriti nešto novo.

533
00:29:12,980 --> 00:29:15,220
[SPEAKER_00] Možda.

534
00:29:15,220 --> 00:29:16,180
[SPEAKER_00] Možda neće.

535
00:29:17,500 --> 00:29:20,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ako se otvori prilika za nešto novo, ja vidim kao pa mogo bi i to.

536
00:29:20,539 --> 00:29:22,119
[SPEAKER_00] Pa dobro, napravi i to.

537
00:29:22,119 --> 00:29:23,900
[SPEAKER_00] A zašto to radiš?

538
00:29:23,900 --> 00:29:26,079
[SPEAKER_00] To zato što mi je važna Bože volja za moj život.

539
00:29:26,079 --> 00:29:28,980
[SPEAKER_00] Znate, zato što mi je važno Bože kraljestvo.

540
00:29:28,980 --> 00:29:31,259
[SPEAKER_00] Želim Bože kraljestvo u svom životu.

541
00:29:31,259 --> 00:29:33,140
[SPEAKER_00] Želim da mi je srce na pravo mjestu.

542
00:29:33,140 --> 00:29:36,200
[SPEAKER_00] Zato ga mi je stalo.

543
00:29:36,740 --> 00:29:37,859
[SPEAKER_00] A šta da onda radim dalje?

544
00:29:37,859 --> 00:29:39,460
[SPEAKER_00] Pa napravi dalje šta vidiš.

545
00:29:39,460 --> 00:29:46,539
[SPEAKER_00] I ja shvatim kad sam dok sam s njim razgovaroio, objašnjavao mu kao koje korake sam napravio.

546
00:29:46,539 --> 00:29:53,440
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao nisam ništa napravio drugo nego ono što sam znao da trebam u tom trenutku.

547
00:29:56,140 --> 00:29:57,380
[SPEAKER_00] Nastavio sam dalje raditi.

548
00:29:57,380 --> 00:29:59,880
[SPEAKER_00] Je li to bila faza gdje sam se ja loše osjećao?

549
00:29:59,880 --> 00:30:00,160
[SPEAKER_00] Je.

550
00:30:00,160 --> 00:30:02,579
[SPEAKER_00] Je li to bila faza gdje sam razmišljio odustat?

551
00:30:02,579 --> 00:30:03,140
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

552
00:30:03,140 --> 00:30:05,160
[SPEAKER_00] Jesam ih imao još?

553
00:30:05,160 --> 00:30:05,619
[SPEAKER_00] Jesam.

554
00:30:05,619 --> 00:30:09,299
[SPEAKER_00] Ali šta sam nastavio?

555
00:30:09,299 --> 00:30:12,079
[SPEAKER_00] Nastavio sam dalje raditi ono što je trebalo.

556
00:30:12,079 --> 00:30:17,259
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto je to danas teško?

557
00:30:17,259 --> 00:30:21,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ima još jedan citad zapravo.

558
00:30:21,440 --> 00:30:23,059
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ovo kaže, sve je vaše.

559
00:30:23,059 --> 00:30:26,059
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo svijet, bilo život, bilo smrt, bilo sadašnjost, bilo budućnost.

560
00:30:26,140 --> 00:30:26,779
[SPEAKER_00] Sve je vaša.

561
00:30:26,779 --> 00:30:28,819
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ste Kristove, a Krist Boži.

562
00:30:28,819 --> 00:30:33,859
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je nevjerojatno fleksibilan što se tiče budućnosti.

563
00:30:33,859 --> 00:30:37,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ali je strog što se tiče sadašnjosti.

564
00:30:37,619 --> 00:30:41,359
[SPEAKER_00] Jer je potpuno jasan što trebaš sad raditi.

565
00:30:41,359 --> 00:30:46,400
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste li poslušan sad u ovom trenutku?

566
00:30:46,400 --> 00:30:50,200
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

567
00:30:50,200 --> 00:30:53,920
[SPEAKER_00] Pa služit ću kad završim ovo i kad mi se posloži.

568
00:30:53,920 --> 00:30:55,519
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ne, sad te zove na služenje.

569
00:30:56,140 --> 00:30:58,819
[SPEAKER_00] Pa trebamo pokopati.

570
00:30:58,819 --> 00:31:00,640
[SPEAKER_00] Pa pusti neka mrtva, pokapo je mrtva.

571
00:31:00,640 --> 00:31:01,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ti kreni za mnom sada.

572
00:31:01,779 --> 00:31:05,700
[SPEAKER_00] Ej, ali znaš šta, kupili smo novog vola, imamo, trebamo isprobati malo.

573
00:31:05,700 --> 00:31:08,619
[SPEAKER_00] Pa pusti nekom, ti sad kreni za mnom.

574
00:31:09,700 --> 00:31:10,539
[SPEAKER_00] To je evanđelje.

575
00:31:10,539 --> 00:31:13,200
[SPEAKER_00] To je evanđelje.

576
00:31:13,200 --> 00:31:17,240
[SPEAKER_00] Fleksibilan je za budućnost, ali za sadašnjost je malo stisnuti.

577
00:31:17,240 --> 00:31:19,660
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto? Zato što za sadašnjost ti je rekao šta da radiš.

578
00:31:19,660 --> 00:31:20,880
[SPEAKER_00] Sad te zovem.

579
00:31:23,039 --> 00:31:25,940
[SPEAKER_00] Kada je došao onaj bogati mladić, šta mi još činiti?

580
00:31:25,940 --> 00:31:27,539
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ide i prodaj sve što imaš.

581
00:31:31,140 --> 00:31:31,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ipak ne.

582
00:31:31,880 --> 00:31:34,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam je sad.

583
00:31:34,039 --> 00:31:36,180
[SPEAKER_00] Sad mi kreni za mnom, sad napravi korak.

584
00:31:36,180 --> 00:31:37,200
[SPEAKER_00] Sad te zovem.

585
00:31:37,200 --> 00:31:39,059
[SPEAKER_00] Poziv je sad, sad vam kažem.

586
00:31:39,059 --> 00:31:39,859
[SPEAKER_00] Poziv je sad.

587
00:31:39,859 --> 00:31:43,720
[SPEAKER_00] Ti sad odlučuješ šta ćeš napraviti i koliko si poslušan.

588
00:31:43,720 --> 00:31:47,039
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ne mogu reći budem dio kasnije.

589
00:31:47,039 --> 00:31:51,099
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, bog ne želi samo jedan duhovni dio našeg vremena

590
00:31:51,099 --> 00:31:52,880
[SPEAKER_00] kada smo mi u njegovoj prisutnosti

591
00:31:52,880 --> 00:31:55,480
[SPEAKER_00] i kada mi, e, sad je ovaj trenutak molitve.

592
00:31:55,480 --> 00:31:57,480
[SPEAKER_00] Moj odnos s njim je neprestan.

593
00:31:57,599 --> 00:32:02,839
[SPEAKER_00] Moj odnos je prožet da ga ja želim proslaviti,

594
00:32:02,839 --> 00:32:05,900
[SPEAKER_00] da ja želim njega u svakom dijelu svog života.

595
00:32:05,900 --> 00:32:09,339
[SPEAKER_00] Ne samo nekom kad smo mi na susretu u zajednici i kad molim.

596
00:32:09,339 --> 00:32:17,920
[SPEAKER_00] Čak idem toliko daleko da

597
00:32:17,920 --> 00:32:21,440
[SPEAKER_00] moj stav za stvari koje ja trebam

598
00:32:21,440 --> 00:32:24,900
[SPEAKER_00] prijatko kada uopće spominjem, Bože,

599
00:32:24,900 --> 00:32:26,660
[SPEAKER_00] znaš šta, riješi mi ovo tu.

600
00:32:27,500 --> 00:32:29,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ili vidiš da mi ovo fali. I daj mi ovo otvori.

601
00:32:29,680 --> 00:32:35,180
[SPEAKER_00] Nego sam u postavci,

602
00:32:35,180 --> 00:32:37,180
[SPEAKER_00] znaš šta, Bože, ja znam šta je tebi važno.

603
00:32:37,180 --> 00:32:39,460
[SPEAKER_00] Tebi je važno da ja doodim danas tamo na vijestin.

604
00:32:39,460 --> 00:32:42,019
[SPEAKER_00] Tebi je važno da ja radim na sebi, da bi mogu to bolje prinjeti.

605
00:32:42,019 --> 00:32:43,559
[SPEAKER_00] Tebi je važno da ja čitam,

606
00:32:43,559 --> 00:32:45,339
[SPEAKER_00] da ja mogu, da te upoznam,

607
00:32:45,339 --> 00:32:47,259
[SPEAKER_00] da mogu to prenositi dalje, da te spoznam.

608
00:32:47,259 --> 00:32:48,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ću te stvari raditi.

609
00:32:48,539 --> 00:32:51,420
[SPEAKER_00] A znaš šta, Bože, ja znam da ti znaš šta je meni važno.

610
00:32:51,420 --> 00:32:53,579
[SPEAKER_00] Meni je važno jer ja sada trebam dići kredit.

611
00:32:53,700 --> 00:32:55,380
[SPEAKER_00] Meni je važno jer ja sada trebam riješiti ovo.

612
00:32:55,380 --> 00:32:57,619
[SPEAKER_00] Meni je važno zato što ja imam ovu tu situaciju.

613
00:32:57,619 --> 00:32:59,940
[SPEAKER_00] Meni je važno zato što imamo ovu diagnozu,

614
00:32:59,940 --> 00:33:02,200
[SPEAKER_00] zato što imamo problema s ovim i zato što imamo ovo.

615
00:33:02,200 --> 00:33:04,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ja znam da ti vidiš da mi je to važno.

616
00:33:04,940 --> 00:33:07,319
[SPEAKER_00] I znaš šta, Bože, ja ću napraviti sve

617
00:33:07,319 --> 00:33:10,819
[SPEAKER_00] za ono što je tebi važno.

618
00:33:10,819 --> 00:33:15,259
[SPEAKER_00] Riješi ono što je meni važno.

619
00:33:15,259 --> 00:33:21,579
[SPEAKER_00] Nema, ja ne znam,

620
00:33:21,579 --> 00:33:24,619
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam pet puta u zadnjih pet godina

621
00:33:24,619 --> 00:33:27,319
[SPEAKER_00] probao neko vrijeme da sam sjedio i molio za svoju nakanu.

622
00:33:29,019 --> 00:33:32,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ne da sam onda samo se sjedio tuđih nakana.

623
00:33:32,279 --> 00:33:36,599
[SPEAKER_00] Nego sve što je usmjereno je bilo usmjereno

624
00:33:36,599 --> 00:33:39,779
[SPEAKER_00] na to, Bože, daj da Tvoju riječ prenesemo što bolje.

625
00:33:39,779 --> 00:33:42,940
[SPEAKER_00] Šta god da radimo.

626
00:33:44,940 --> 00:33:47,019
[SPEAKER_00] I onda ispada neko da o poslu samo razmišlja.

627
00:33:47,019 --> 00:33:49,019
[SPEAKER_00] Molim za one posla koje mi ide.

628
00:33:49,019 --> 00:33:51,700
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ne, njemu je to važno.

629
00:33:51,700 --> 00:33:55,359
[SPEAKER_00] Okej, Bože, meni je Tvoja stvar važna.

630
00:33:55,359 --> 00:33:57,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ću se pozabaviti s Tvojim stvarima.

631
00:33:57,680 --> 00:33:59,299
[SPEAKER_00] Molim te riješi moje stvari.

632
00:33:59,299 --> 00:34:01,819
[SPEAKER_00] Tu su i za tebe.

633
00:34:01,819 --> 00:34:02,859
[SPEAKER_00] Riješi ih.

634
00:34:02,859 --> 00:34:04,660
[SPEAKER_00] I osjećaj, nekaj si razmišljam,

635
00:34:04,660 --> 00:34:09,340
[SPEAKER_00] možda bi trebao više probijati,

636
00:34:09,340 --> 00:34:10,360
[SPEAKER_00] možda bi trebao više moliti,

637
00:34:10,360 --> 00:34:11,860
[SPEAKER_00] možda bi trebao, ne znam.

638
00:34:11,860 --> 00:34:13,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, znaš šta?

639
00:34:14,940 --> 00:34:15,980
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš šta mi je važno?

640
00:34:15,980 --> 00:34:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] Imam to, to spomenut ću nekada.

641
00:34:17,539 --> 00:34:19,159
[SPEAKER_00] Bila je nedavno situacija,

642
00:34:19,159 --> 00:34:21,579
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam, imao sam nedavno razgovor

643
00:34:21,579 --> 00:34:24,079
[SPEAKER_00] i razmišljao sam o tome

644
00:34:24,079 --> 00:34:26,460
[SPEAKER_00] i onda sam pričao osobi i kažem,

645
00:34:26,460 --> 00:34:28,860
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo, sad sve što se događa

646
00:34:28,860 --> 00:34:29,960
[SPEAKER_00] je bio trenutak.

647
00:34:29,960 --> 00:34:32,039
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo je ovo ljeto, kraj ljeta,

648
00:34:32,039 --> 00:34:33,179
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam bio u jednoj fazi

649
00:34:33,179 --> 00:34:34,019
[SPEAKER_00] i razmišljao sam si,

650
00:34:34,019 --> 00:34:36,199
[SPEAKER_00] ne, ma trebam ja nešto drugo,

651
00:34:36,199 --> 00:34:37,420
[SPEAKER_00] trebam ja nešto dodatno,

652
00:34:37,420 --> 00:34:38,360
[SPEAKER_00] trebam ja nešto novo.

653
00:34:38,360 --> 00:34:39,739
[SPEAKER_00] Imao sam ja super ideju

654
00:34:39,739 --> 00:34:41,019
[SPEAKER_00] i kažem, Mirjani, znaš šta,

655
00:34:41,199 --> 00:34:41,960
[SPEAKER_00] ovo je super ideja,

656
00:34:41,960 --> 00:34:43,280
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da bi mogu krenut ovo.

657
00:34:43,280 --> 00:34:44,300
[SPEAKER_00] I ona meni kaže,

658
00:34:44,300 --> 00:34:44,920
[SPEAKER_00] može, Marko,

659
00:34:44,920 --> 00:34:45,980
[SPEAKER_00] ali onda ostavljaš Ehov.

660
00:34:45,980 --> 00:34:49,280
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam tako mislio,

661
00:34:49,280 --> 00:34:49,840
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam mislio,

662
00:34:49,840 --> 00:34:50,619
[SPEAKER_00] kao, ma nema šanse,

663
00:34:50,619 --> 00:34:52,019
[SPEAKER_00] ne možeš ići na dvije fronte,

664
00:34:52,019 --> 00:34:52,820
[SPEAKER_00] ne, ne možeš to,

665
00:34:52,820 --> 00:34:53,880
[SPEAKER_00] bireš šta hoćeš.

666
00:34:53,880 --> 00:34:54,880
[SPEAKER_00] Kao, i pita me,

667
00:34:54,880 --> 00:34:56,139
[SPEAKER_00] Marko, još si se pomolio?

668
00:34:56,139 --> 00:34:58,920
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao, pa jesam?

669
00:34:58,920 --> 00:34:59,679
[SPEAKER_00] Kao, pa dobro,

670
00:34:59,679 --> 00:35:00,380
[SPEAKER_00] šta ti je Bog rekao?

671
00:35:00,380 --> 00:35:03,360
[SPEAKER_00] Pa rekao mi je i sad.

672
00:35:03,360 --> 00:35:04,659
[SPEAKER_00] Šta mi je Bog rekao?

673
00:35:04,659 --> 00:35:06,360
[SPEAKER_00] Bog mi rekao tada,

674
00:35:06,360 --> 00:35:07,559
[SPEAKER_00] podsjetio me na jedan citat

675
00:35:07,559 --> 00:35:09,059
[SPEAKER_00] koji godinama nisam pročitao.

676
00:35:09,059 --> 00:35:12,059
[SPEAKER_00] Već sam ga spomenuo nekad ovdje,

677
00:35:12,059 --> 00:35:13,960
[SPEAKER_00] kada je Natan rekao Davidu,

678
00:35:13,960 --> 00:35:15,579
[SPEAKER_00] kada je sagriješio sa Bat Šebom,

679
00:35:15,579 --> 00:35:17,059
[SPEAKER_00] kada mu je rekao,

680
00:35:17,059 --> 00:35:19,460
[SPEAKER_00] sve sam ti dao.

681
00:35:19,460 --> 00:35:20,619
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže Bog Davidu,

682
00:35:20,619 --> 00:35:21,500
[SPEAKER_00] sve sam ti dao.

683
00:35:21,500 --> 00:35:23,860
[SPEAKER_00] I da ti je to bilo malo

684
00:35:23,860 --> 00:35:26,039
[SPEAKER_00] i da si me tražio još,

685
00:35:26,039 --> 00:35:27,539
[SPEAKER_00] ja bi ti dao još.

686
00:35:27,539 --> 00:35:29,599
[SPEAKER_00] I kad sam to izgovaro,

687
00:35:29,599 --> 00:35:30,039
[SPEAKER_00] Mirjani,

688
00:35:30,039 --> 00:35:31,280
[SPEAKER_00] šta mi je rekao?

689
00:35:32,219 --> 00:35:33,079
[SPEAKER_00] Knedla u grlu,

690
00:35:33,079 --> 00:35:34,059
[SPEAKER_00] ja u suzama,

691
00:35:34,059 --> 00:35:35,400
[SPEAKER_00] kao,

692
00:35:35,400 --> 00:35:36,239
[SPEAKER_00] sve mi je jasno.

693
00:35:36,239 --> 00:35:37,420
[SPEAKER_00] I znate šta se dogodilo?

694
00:35:37,420 --> 00:35:38,619
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon toga,

695
00:35:38,619 --> 00:35:39,320
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam rekao,

696
00:35:39,320 --> 00:35:40,019
[SPEAKER_00] okej,

697
00:35:40,019 --> 00:35:40,840
[SPEAKER_00] jasno mi je.

698
00:35:40,840 --> 00:35:42,539
[SPEAKER_00] Neću filozofirati,

699
00:35:42,539 --> 00:35:43,780
[SPEAKER_00] neću izmišljati o toplu vodu.

700
00:35:43,780 --> 00:35:44,760
[SPEAKER_00] Bože,

701
00:35:44,760 --> 00:35:45,739
[SPEAKER_00] malo mi je,

702
00:35:45,739 --> 00:35:46,559
[SPEAKER_00] želim još.

703
00:35:46,559 --> 00:35:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mjesec dana nakon toga,

704
00:35:51,000 --> 00:35:52,860
[SPEAKER_00] pokreću se stvari,

705
00:35:52,860 --> 00:35:54,420
[SPEAKER_00] pokreću se nove stvari,

706
00:35:54,420 --> 00:35:55,880
[SPEAKER_00] počinje se zavrtiti

707
00:35:55,880 --> 00:35:57,260
[SPEAKER_00] jedna nova priča,

708
00:35:57,260 --> 00:35:58,460
[SPEAKER_00] za tri mjeseca,

709
00:35:58,460 --> 00:35:59,519
[SPEAKER_00] nitko ne vjeruje

710
00:35:59,519 --> 00:36:00,800
[SPEAKER_00] zašto se to tako dogodilo,

711
00:36:00,800 --> 00:36:01,880
[SPEAKER_00] šta se trebno događa,

